{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/jCrMCnpQvCJOgEW4stUtbSBm17B.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Drama"},{"id":36,"name":"History"}],"homepage":"https://le-pacte.com/international/film/the-great-arch","id":1290424,"imdb_id":"tt32398150","origin_country":["FR"],"original_language":"fr","original_title":"L'Inconnu de la Grande Arche","overview":"France, 1983. The biggest architectural competition in history is launched by the new socialist president, François Mitterrand. Coveted by all the biggest international architectural firms, the open-call competition is surprisingly won by an unknown: Johan Otto von Spreckelsen, an architecture teacher from Copenhagen. Until then, the fifty-year-old Dane had built only four buildings: his home, and three small chapels.","popularity":3.4084,"poster_path":"/zriwECvMyJNcUdXrELeYSrXF0f2.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":207,"logo_path":"/uskenzq65wJe0cT0D8StQI3hJnO.png","name":"Agat Films & Cie / Ex Nihilo","origin_country":"FR"},{"id":591,"logo_path":"/q5I5RDwMEiqoNmfaJgd2LraEOJY.png","name":"France 3 Cinéma","origin_country":"FR"},{"id":5125,"logo_path":"/t3oWTsVukmEzrZzvfr37XRBibo5.png","name":"Le Pacte","origin_country":"FR"},{"id":76,"logo_path":"/nebkQYtQKhZyHJfh5v0oGpNbPzu.png","name":"Zentropa Entertainments","origin_country":"DK"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"FR","name":"France"},{"iso_3166_1":"DK","name":"Denmark"}],"release_date":"2025-11-05","revenue":0,"runtime":104,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English"},{"english_name":"Danish","iso_639_1":"da","name":"Dansk"},{"english_name":"French","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français"},{"english_name":"Italian","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"The Great Arch","video":false,"vote_average":7.0,"vote_count":73,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","title":"The Great Arch","type":""},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","title":"El Arquitecto